When setting R for jupyter notebook, 
you have to install "IRkernel" and launch it with the following command, IRkernel::installspec().

If you receive the following message, do as follow. 
"Error in IRkernel::installspec() :
jupyter-client has to be installed but “jupyter kernelspec –version” exited with code 127."

Solution)
My Computer -> right click -> Properties -> Advanced System Setting -> Environmental Variable -> Edit “Path” 
-> add “C:\Users\User\Anaconda3”, “C:\Users\User\Anaconda3\Scripts”, “C:\Users\User\Anaconda3\Library\bin”
